hadiths[99]{hadithnumber,text}:
778,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to Ansaar ney kaha : eik ameer hum mein sey hoga aur eik tum (muhajrin) mein sey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas aaye aur farmaya : kya tum jantey nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya tha ke wo logon ko namaz padhaaeyn. to tum mein sey kon chaheyga ke Abu-Bakar sey aagey badhey? unhoney kaha : hum is baat sey Allah ki panah talab kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey aagay badheyn."
779,"Hazrat Abul Aaliyaa Baraa ney kaha ke eik din Ziyad (governer Koofa aur Basra) ney namaz ko muakhkhar (deri) kiya to merey paas Abdullah bin Saamit aaye, mainey unkey liye kursi rakhi. wo is par beth gaey. mainey un sey Ziyad key is kaam ka zikr kya to unhoney apney hont kaatey aur meri raan par haath maara aur kehney lagey : mainey Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye masla puchha tha jaisaey ke tu ney mujh sey puchha hai to unhoney meri raan par isi tarah haath maara tha jis tarah mainey teri raan par maara hai aur farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye masla puchha tha jaisa ke tu ney mujh sey puchha hai to aap ney bhi meri raan par haath maara tha jis tarah mainey teri raan par maara hai aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : waqt par namaz padh lena phir agar un (muakhkhar karney walon) key sath namaz paa-ley to unkey sath bhi padh lena. ye na kehna ke mainey namaz padh li hai, lihaza main (unkey sath) nahin padhunga."
780,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Shayad tum aisey logon ko paao jo be-waqt namaz padheyngey. agar tum par aisa daur aa jaey to namaz waqt par padh liya karna phir unkey sath bhi padh lena aur usey nafl samajh lena."
781,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ki imaamat wo shakhs kiraey jo un mein sey Allah Taala ki kitab ko ziyada padhney wala ho. agar wo qirat mein barabar hun to jisney pehley hijrat ki ho. agar wo hijrat mein bhi barabar hon to jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko ziyada janta ho. agar sunnat key ilm mein bhi barabar hon to jo umr mein bada ho. aur to kisi shakhs ki saltanat aur ikhtiyar mein uski imaamat na kara aur na uski musnad izzat par beth magar ye ke wo tujhey ijazat dey."
782,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke main aur mera eik chacha zaad bhai ya sathi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to aap ney farmaya, jab safar mein namaz ka waqt ho jaey to Azan kehna aur jo tum mein bada ho wo imaamat karaaey."
783,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab teen aadmi hon to un mein sey eik imaamat kiraey aur imaamat ka ziyada haq daar un mein sey wo hai jo un mein sey ziyada Quran padhney wala ho."
784,Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi saahibe iqtidar shakhs ki saltanat mein uski imaamat na karaai jaey aur na uski musnade-khaas par betha jaey magar uski ijazat sey.
785,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye ittilaa pahunchi ke banu Amr bin Auf (ehale Qubaa) key darmiyan kuchh jhagda huwa hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey darmiyan suleh karwaaney key liye nikley. aap key sath kuchh aur log bhi they. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wahan der ho gaee aur Zohar ki namaz ka waqt ho gaya. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Abu-Bakar ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) to wahan ruk gaey hain aur namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai to kya aap logon ko namaz padhaaengey? wo farmaney lagey : agar tum chaho to theek hai. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kahi. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey aur Allahu Akbar kaha. (itney mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye aur safon mein sey guzartey huye pehli saf mein aa khadey huye. (Hazrat Abu-Bakar ko mutawajjeh karney key liye) logon ney taaliyan bajaana shuru kar din. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) namaz mein idhar udhar tawajjoh nahin kartey they. jab logon ney kasrat sey aisa kiya to unhoney tawajjoh farmaee. wahan Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey they. Rasulullah ney unhein isharay sey hukm diya ke namaz padhatey rahen magar Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney haath uthaey aur Allah ki hamd aur tareef ki (ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein imaamat key laaiq samjha) aur ultey paaun peechhey hat aaye aur saf mein mil gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aagey badhey aur logon ko namaz padhaai. jab farigh huye to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : aey logo ! tumhein kya huwa? jab tumhein namaz mein koi zarurat pesh aai to tum ney taliyan bajana shuru kar den. (aisi surat mein) taali bajaney ka hukm to aurton key liye hai. jis aadmi ko namaz mein koi hajat pesh aaye to (Imam ko mutawajjeh karney key liye) wo Subhan Allah padhi. (Allah pak hai) kahe. junhi koi usey Subhan Allah padhi. kehta suneyga uski taraf mutawajjeh hoga. (phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ) aey Abu-Bakar ! tujhey namaz padhaaney sey kon si chiz rukaawat hui jab ke mainey tujhey ishara kar diya tha? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Abu-Qahaafa key betey (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ko laaiq na tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein jamaat kiraey (aur aap sey aagey khada ho).
786,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aakhiri namaz jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon key sath padhi wo aap ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey eik kapdey mein padhi thi jisey aap ney apney jism par lapet rakha tha.
787,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon ko namaz padhaai jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) saf mein they.
788,Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna : jab tum mein sey koi doosrey logon sey milney jaey to unhein namaz na padhaaey.
789,Hazrat Mehmood bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) apni qom ki imaamat karatey they aur wo naa-beena they. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke kabhi andhera barish ya baarishi pani hota hai aur main na-bina shakhs hun (aisi haalat mein masjid nahin ja sakta) lihaza aap merey ghar main eik jagah namaz ada farmaain jisey main apni namaz key liye muqarrar kar lun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : tum kahan chahtey ho ke main namaz padhun? to unhoney ghar main eik jagah ki taraf ishara kiya. wahan Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi.
790,"Hazrat Amr bin Salma Jurmi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke qafley hamarey paas sey guzra kartey they. hum un sey Quran seekh letey they. merey walid mohtaram Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas (apni qom ka numaainda ban kar) gaey. (wapsi key waqt) aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey imaamat wo kiraey jo ziyada Quran padha huwa ho. merey walid wapis aaye aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhari imaamat wo shakhs kiraey jo Quran ziyada padha huwa ho. logon ney talash kiya to main un sab sey ziyada Quran padha huwa tha, lihaza main un ki imaamat karata tha, halanke main aath saal ka tha."
791,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz ki iqaamat kahi jaey to khadey na ho yahan tak ke mujhey (aata) dekh lo.
792,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa namaz ki iqaamat ho gaee jab ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi sey baaten kar rahey they, chunanche aap jamaat key liye khadey na huye yahan tak ke log so gaey."
793,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke namaz ki iqaamat ho gaee logon ney saffen durust kar lein aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaye yahan tak ke jab aap apney musalley par khadey ho gaey to aap ko yad aaya ke mainey (farz) ghusl nahin kiya. aap ney logon sey farmaya : apni apni jagah thehrey raho. phir aap ghar tashrif ley gaey. wapis lotey to aap key sar mubarak sey pani key qatrey gir rahey they (yani ghusl farma kar aaye they). jab ke hum isi tarah safon mein khadey rahey.
794,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke banu Amr bin Auf mein ladaai jhagda ho gaya. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap Zohar ki namaz padhney key baad un mein suleh karwaaney tashrif ley gaey phir aap ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : aey Bilal ! agar Asr ka waqt ho jaey aur main na aa sakun to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kehna ke wo logon ko namaz padha den. jab namaz ka waqt ho gaya to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Azan kahi phir iqaamat kahi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aagey tashrif laaiye. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey aur namaz shuru kar di. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. aap logon mein sey guzartey huye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey ja khadey huye. logon ney taliyan bajaana shuru kar den. aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jab namaz shuru kar letey they to idhar udhar tawajjoh na farmatey they. lekin jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney dekha ke taliyan ruk hi nahin rahin to unhoney tawajjoh ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath sey unhein ishara kiya ke namaz padhatey rahen lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key us (haali) farman par Allah ka shukar ada kiya phir ultey paaun chaltey huye peechhey hat aaye. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye soorate-haal dekhi to aagey badhey aur logon ko namaz padhaai. jab namaz puri kar li to farmaya : aey Abu-Bakar ! tujhey kon si chiz  ne roka ke tu ney jamaat jari na rakhi jab ke mainey tujhey ishara kar diya tha? unhoney kaha : Abu-Qahaafa key betey key liye munasib na tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki imaamat karaaey. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon sey farmaya : jab tumhein (Imam ko mutawajjeh karney ki) koi zarurat pesh aaye to mard Subhan Allah padhi. kahin aur aurten taali bajaaeyn.
795,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik ghodey sey apney daeyn pehlu par gir padey. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhu aap ki bimar pursi key liye aap key yahaan hazir huye. namaz ka waqt ho gaya. jab aap ney namaz mukammal kar li to farmaya : Imam is liye banaya jata hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey lihaza jab wo rukoo mein chala jaey to tum rukoo karo jab sar utha ley to tum sar uthaao. jab sajda key liye ja chukey to tum sajda karo. aur jab wo (سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ) ( Allah ney us shakhs ki baat sun li jisney uski tareef ki) kahe to tum (ربنا لک الحمد) (aey hamarey Rab ! terey hi liye tareef hai) kaho.
796,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dekha ke aap key as-haab kuchh peechhey peechhey rehtey hain (saff awwal mein shareek nahin hotey). aap ney farmaya : aagey badho (saff awwal mein khadey huwa karo) aur meri iqtida (pairvi) kiya karo. tum sey peechhey khadey honey waley tumhari iqtida (pairvi) kerengey aur kuchh log aisey hain jo (agli safon sey) peechhey hi rehtey hain yahan tak ke Allah Taala bhi unhein (apni rehmat, apney Fazal aur bulandi darjaat waghera mein) peechhey kar deta hai."
797,Abdullah bin Mubarak ney Jareeri sey unhoney Abu-Nazara sey isi tarah (is riwayat key hum maani) bayan kiya.
798,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke logon ko namaz padhaeyn. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey aagey they, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney beth kar namaz padhi. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon ko namaz padhaai aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey they."
799,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein Zohar ki namaz padhaai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechhey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) takbir kehtey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hamein sunaney key liye takbir kehtey.
800,Hazrat Aswad aur Alqama bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas dophare key waqt hazir huye. unhoney farmaya : tehqiq (woh waqt) qarib hai ke aisey Ameer hongey jo namaz key waqt (aur kamon mein) masroof rahengey chunanche tum namaz waqt par padh liya karo phir wo uthey aur hamarey darmiyan khadey ho kar namaz padhaai aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai.
801,Hazrat Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas sey guzrey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar mujhey kehney lagey : aey Masood ! apney Aaqa Abu Tameem key paas jaao aur un sey kaho ke wo hamein sawari key liye eik oont den. kuchh kharch bhi bhejein aur eik rehnuma bhi sath kar den jo hamein Madiney ki raah batlaaey. main apney aaqa key paas aaya aur unhein pegham pahunchaya to unhoney merey haath eik oont aur doodh ka eik mishkizaa bheja (aur mujhey rehnuma bana diya). main unhein poshida raastey sey ley chala. namaz ka waqt ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar namaz padhaaney lagey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap key daeyn khadey ho gaey. us waqt tak main bhi Islam qubul kar chuka tha. (is liye) main un dono key sath aaya. main unkey peechhey khada ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Abu-Bakar key seeney par haath maara (ke wo peechhey hat kar merey sath khadey ho jaeyn) phir hum dono aap key peechhey khadey huye. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (sanad mein mazkur) ye Barida hadees mein qawi nahin (yani zaeef hai).
802,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke un ki daadi Muleka (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khaney ki dawat di jo unhoney aap key liye tayyar kiya tha. aap ney is mein sey kuchh khaya phir farmaya : utho ! main tumhein namaz padhaaun. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main apni eik chataai ki taraf utha jo ziyada istimal ki wajeh sey siyah ho chuki thi. mainey is par pani dala. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey. mainey aur eik yatim ney aap key peechhey saf banai aur budhiya (daadi mohtarma) hamarey peechhey khadi huin. aap ney hamein do rakatein padhaain phir aap tashrif ley gaey.
803,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahaan tashrif laye. hum ghar waley sirf main, meri walida, eik yatim ladka aur meri khaala Ummey Haram (Raziallahu anhu) hi they. aap ney farmaya : utho ! main tumhein namaz padhaaun. halanke kisi farz namaz ka waqt na tha phir aap ney hamein namaz padhaai."
804,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur meri walida aur khaala namaz padhney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz padhaai. mujhey apney daeyn aur meri walida aur khaala ko peechhey khada kiya.
805,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath khadey ho kar namaz padhi aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) hamarey peechhey khadi huin. wo bhi hamarey sath hi namaz (baa-jamaa't) padh rahi thin jab ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key pehlu mein aap key sath (baa-jamaa't) namaz padh raha tha.
806,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aur merey deegar ghar walon mein sey eik aurat ko is tarah namaz padhaai ke mujhey apni daeyn taraf khada kiya aur aurat ko peechhey.
807,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey apni khaala Memuna (Ummul-Mominin) (Raziallahu anha) key yahaan raat guzari. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko namaz (tahajjud) padhney key liye uthey to main aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya. aap ney mujhey is tarah sar sey pakda aur daeyn taraf khada kar liya.
808,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey qabl hamarey kandhon ko pakad pakad kar sidha kartey they aur farmatey they : aagey peechhey khadey na huwa karo warna tumharey dil bhi eik doosrey sey bigad jaeyngey (un mein phoot pad jaaeygi). merey qarib tum mein sey samajh daar (baligh) aur aql-mand log khadey hon phir wo log jo un sey qarib hain, phir wo log jo un sey qarib hain. Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : aaj tum mein sakht ikhtilaf hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain : (sanad mein mazkur) Abu-Ma'mar ka naam Abdullah bin Sakhbara hai."
809,Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa main masjid mein pehli saf mein tha. mujhey merey peechhey sey eik aadmi ney khincha aur mujhey peechhey kar diya aur khud meri jagah khada ho gaya. Allah ki qism ! (mujhey is qadr ghussa aaya ke) main apni namaz bhi tawajjoh sey na padh saka. jab wo shakhs farigh huwa to mainey dekha wo Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) they. kehney lagey : aey jawan ! Allah Taala tujhey har takleef sey bachaey. tehqiq ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki hamein nasihat hai ke hum (samajh-daar aur badi umr key log) aap key qarib (pehli saf mein) khadey hon. phir aap (Abi bin Kaab) qibley ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur teen dafa farmaya : Kabey key Rab ki qism ! ehale hal w aqd log halak ho gaey. phir farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey un par afsos nahin balke afsos un par hai jinhonney unhein gumrah kiya. mainey kaha : aey Abu Yaaqoob ! aap ehale hal w aqd sey kya murad letey hain? farmaya : Ameer yani hukkaam.
810,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jamaat ki iqaamat ho gaee to hum khadey ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki tashrif aawri sey qabl saffen durust kar li gaeen. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye yahan tak ke jab apni namaaz gaah mein khadey ho gaey to takbire-tahreema sey qabl hi aap wapis mudey aur hum sey farmaya : apni jagah khadey raho. hum khadey intizar kartey rahey yahan tak ke aap tashrif laye to aap nahaaey huye they aur aap key sar mubarak sey pani key qatrey gir rahey they. phir aap ney takbire-tahreema kahi aur namaz padhaai.
811,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) safon ko aisey sidha farmatey they jaisey teer sidhey kiye jatey hain. phir aap ney eik aadmi ko dekha ke us ka Sina saf sey aagey nikla huwa tha. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap farma rahey they : yaqinan tum apni safon ko sidha karogey warna Allah Taala zarur tumharey chehron key darmiyan mukhalifat dal deyga."
812,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (takbire-tahreema kehney sey qabl) eik sirey sey doosrey sirey tak safon key darmiyan chala kartey they. hamarey kandhon aur seenon ko haathon sey pakad pakad kar sidha kartey aur farmatey they : aagey peechhey khadey na ho'o warna tumharey dil eik doosrey sey mukhtalif ho jaeyngey (un mein phoot pad jaeygi). aur aap farmatey they : tehqiq Allah Taala agli safon key liye khususi rahmatein nazil farmata hai. aur uskey farishtey unkey liye khususi rahmatein talab kartey hain.
813,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey kandhon ko pakadtey aur farmatey : sidhey ho jaao aur aagey peechhey na khadey ho'o warna tumharey dil badal jaeyngey (un mein phoot pad jaeygi). aur merey qarib tum mein sey aql-mand (baligh) aur samajh-daar log khadey hon, phir wo log jo un sey qarib hain, phir wo log jo un sey qarib hain."
814,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) teen dafa farmaya kartey they : barabar ho jaao. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tehqiq main tumhein apney peechhey sey bhi isi tarah dekhta hun jaisey tumhein samney sey dekhta hun.
815,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) takbire-tahreema kehney sey qabl hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : apni safen sidhi karo aur mil kar khadey ho'o kyonkey main tumhein apney peechhey sey bhi dekhta hun.
816,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni safon ko milaao (yani mil kar khadey ho'o aur inhein qarib qarib banaao yani in mein fasla kam rakho aur gardanen eik seedh mein rakho. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! main shayatin ko dekhta hun ke wo safon key shigaaf (daraar) mein is tarah dakhil hotey hain jaisey ke wo bhaid bakriyon key bachchey hain."
817,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamari taraf tashrif laye aur farmaya : tum is tarah saf bandi kyon nahin kartey jis tarah farishtey apney Rab taala key yahaan saf bandi kartey hain? sahaba ney puchha : farishtey apney Rab key paas kaisey saf bandi kartey hain? aap ney farmaya : (pehley) saf awwal ko pura kartey hain, isi ke sath safon mein mil kar khadey hotey hain."
818,Hazrat Arbaaz bin Saariyaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) pehli saf key liye teen dafa dua farmatey they aur dusri saf key liye eik dafa.
819,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pehli saf mukammal karo, phir wo jo us (pehli) sey mili hui hai (dusri). agar koi kami ho to wo aakhiri saf mein honi chahiye (na ke pehli saf mein)."
820,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo koi saf ko milaaeyga Allah Taala usey (apney sath) milaaeyga aur jo saf ko kaatey (todey) ga Allah Taala usey kaatey (todey) ga."
821,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mardon ki behtareen saf pehli saf hai aur bad-tareen saf aakhiri saf hai. aur aurton ki behtareen saf aakhiri saf hai aur bad-tareen saf pehli saf hai (jo mardon sey mili hui ho)."
822,Hazrat Abdul-Hameed bin Mehmood bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath they. hamney hukkaam mein sey eik haakim key sath namaz padhi. logon ney hamein dhakel diya yahan tak ke hum khadey huye aur do sutonon key darmiyan namaz padhi. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sutonon wali saf sey peechhey hatney lagey aur farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein us (sutonon key darmiyan saf bananey) sey bacha kartey they.
823,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke hum jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey namaz padhtey they to meri khahish hoti thi ke main aap ki daeyn taraf khada hun.
824,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi logon ko namaz padhaaey to halki padhaaey kyonkey un mein bimar kamzor aur boodhey bhi hotey hain, albatta jab wo akela namaz padhey to jis qadr chahey lambi padhey."
825,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sab logon sey halki magar mukammal namaz padhatey they.
826,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kabhi-kabhi main namaz mein khada hota hun, phir kisi bachchey key roney ki aawaz sunta hun to namaz ko mukhtasar kar deta hun ke uski maa par mashaqqat ka sabab na ban jaaun."
827,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz halki padhaaney ka hukm detey they magar khud Sura صافات key sath hamari imaamat farmatey.
828,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap logon ki imaamat kara rahey they jab ke aap ney Umaama binte Abul-Aas ko apney kandhey par uthaya huwa tha. jab aap rukoo farmatey to usey utaar detey aur jab sajdey key baad uthtey to usey dobara utha letey."
829,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Imam sey pehley apna sar utha leta hai, kya wo is baat sey darta nahin ke Allah Taala us ka sar gadhey key sar jaisa bana dey."
830,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aur wo jhootey na they, ke jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhtey they aur aap rukoo sey sar uthatey to Sahaba khadey rehtey yahan tak ke aap ko dekh letey ke aap sajdey mein chaley gaey hain to phir sajda kartey."
831,"Hazrat Hitaan bin Abdullah bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein namaz padhaai. jab wo (aakhiri) qaaedey mein they to eik aadmi dakhil huwa aur us ney kaha : namaz ko neki aur Zakat sey milaya gaya hai. jab Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney salam pheraa to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tum mein sey kis ney ye baat kahi hai? log khamosh rahey. aap farmaney lagey : aey Hitaan ! shayad tum ney ye baat kahi hai? mainey kaha : nahin. wesey mujhey khatra tha ke aap mujhey hi is baat par daantengey. aap ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hamari namaz aur doosrey tareeqey sikhaey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam is liye hota hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, chunanche jab wo (Allah Akbar) keh ley to tum (Allah Akbar) kaho aur jab wo (غیر المغضوب علیھم wala الضالین) keh ley to tum padhi. Aameen padhi. kaho. Allah Taala tumhari dua qubul farmaeyga. aur jab Imam rukoo mein chala jaey to tum rukoo karo. aur jab wo sar uthaey aur kahe (سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ) to tum kaho : (ربنا لک الحمد) Allah Taala tumhari hamd suneyga. aur jab wo sajdey mein chala jaey, to tum sajda karo. aur jab wo sar utha ley to phir tum sar uthaao. Imam tum sey pehley sajdey mein jata hai aur tum sey pehley sar uthata hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye jaldi sar uthana jaldi janey key muqabley mein hai (yani idhar ki kasar udhar nikal qaee)."
832,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Ansaar mein sey eik aadmi aaya jab ke jamaat khadi ho chuki thi. wo masjid mein aaya aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey namaz padhney laga. unhoney namaz lambi kar di. wo aadmi (safon sey) nikal gaya aur us ney masjid key eik koney mein namaz padhi, phir chala gaya. jab Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) namaz sey farigh huye to unhein bataya gaya ke falan shakhs ney aisey aisey kiya hai. Hazrat Muaz ney kaha : agar mujhey subah nasib hui to main ye baat zarur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan karunga. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey aur aap sey us waaqiey ka zikr kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aadmi ko bula bheja aur farmaya : tujhey kis chiz ney is kaam par aamada kiya? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main sara din oont par pani dhota raha. main aaya to jamaat khadi thi. main masjid mein dakhil huwa aur unkey sath namaz mein shamil ho gaya to unhoney falan falan sura (Soora- Baqraa) shuru kar di aur bahut lambi qirat ki. mainey namaz tod kar masjid key eik koney mein alag namaz padh li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Muaz ! kya to logon ko fitney mein dal raha hai? aey Muaz ! kya to logon ko sakht takleef mein mubtala kar raha hai? aey Muaz ! kya to logon ko aazmaaish mein dal raha hai?"
833,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik ghodey par sawar huye to us sey gir gaey aur aap ka daayan pehlu chhil gaya. aap ney koi eik namaz beth kar padhi. hamney bhi aap key peechhey beth kar namaz padhi. jab aap farigh huye to farmaya : Imam is liye banaya gaya hai ke uski perwi ki jaey, lihaza jab wo khada ho kar namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar namaz padho. jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo. jab wo (سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ) kahe to tum (ربنا لک الحمد) kaho aur jab wo beth kar namaz padhey to tum bhi beth kar namaz padho."
834,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ziyada bimar huye to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ko namaz ki ittilaa deney aaye. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Bakar sey kaho ke logon ko namaz padhaeyn. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Abu-Bakar bahut naram dil aadmi hain. jab wo aap ki jagah khadey hongey to (roney ki wajeh sey) logon ko qirat na suna sakengey. agar aap Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm den (to achhi baat hai). aap ney farmaya : (nahin) Abu-Bakar sey kaho : logon ko namaz padhaeyn. mainey Hafsa sey kaha : tum bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaho. unhoney bhi aap sey kaha. aap ney farmaya : tum Hazrat Yusuf alehissalam key waqiey wali aurton ki tarah ho. Abu-Bakar sey kaho logon ko namaz padhaaeyn. logon ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha. phir jab unhoney namaz shuru ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney aap main kuch aaram aur ifaaqa (faayda) mehsus kiya. aap uthey. do aadmiyon key darmiyan aap ko unkey kandhon key saharey chalaya gaya. phir bhi aap key paaun mubarak zamin par ghisat rahey they (aap mein paaun uthaney ki sakat (taaqat) na thi ). jab aap masjid mein dakhil huye to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki aahat mehsus kar key peechhey hatney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ishara farmaya ke isi tarah khadey rahen. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baain janib beth gaey, chunanche Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) beth kar logon ko namaz padha rahey they aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar aap ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they."
835,"Ubedullah bin Abdullah sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur kaha : kya aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key marzul-maut key barey mein bayan nahin farmaatin? wo farmaney lagin : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ziyada bimar ho gaey to farmaney lagey : kya logon ney namaz padh li hai? hamney kaha : nahin, wo aap ka intizar kar rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : merey liye tab mein pani dalo. hamney taameel ki. aap ney ghusl farmaya (taake bukhaar ki shiddat (garmi) kam ho). phir aap ney uthney ka irada kiya to be-hosh ho gaey. phir hosh mein aaye to farmaney lagey : kya logon ney namaz padh li hai? hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! nahin, balke wo aap ka intizar kar rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : merey liye tab mein pani rakho. hamney taameel ki. aap ney phir ghusl kiya aur uthney ka irada kiya magar dobara be-hosh ho gaey. phir teesri dafa bhi aisey hi farmaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : log masjid mein bethey Isha ki namaz key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka intizar kar rahey they. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham bhej diya ke logon ko namaz padhaaeyn. qaasid unkey paas aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aap ko hukm dey rahey hain ke logon ko namaz padhaaeyn. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) naram dil aadmi they. kehney lagey : aey umr ! tum namaz padhaao. unhoney kaha : aap hi is izzat (Imaamat) key sab sey ziyada haq daar hain. phir un dino mein Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney namazeyn padhaaeyn. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni tabiat mein ifaaqa sukun mehsus kiya to aap namaze-Zohar key liye do aadmiyon key saharey tashrif laye. un do aadmiyon mein sey eik Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) they. jab aap ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney dekha to wo peechhey hatney lagey. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ishara farmaya ke peechhey na haten. aur aap ney (laney waley) un do aadmiyon ko hukm diya to unhoney aap ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baain janib bitha diya. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar namaz padhtey rahey. log Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaz key sath namaz padhtey rahey jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) beth kar namaz padhtey rahey. Ubedullah ney kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas gaya aur mainey kaha : kya main aap par wo riwayat pesh na karun jo mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key marzul-maut key barey mein bayan ki hai? unhoney kaha : haan. mainey puri riwayat bayan ki. unhoney kisi bhi lafz ka inkar nahin kiya magar unhoney kaha : kya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney tujhey us aadmi ka naam bataya jo Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath (aap ko sahara deney waley ) they? mainey kaha : nahin. unhoney farmaya : wo Hazrat Ali (karam Allah wajha) they."
836,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhtey they, phir apni qom ki taraf wapis jatey aur un ki imaamat karatey they. eik raat aap ney namaz muakhkhar (deri) ki. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi, phir apni qom ko namaz padhaaney key liye un ki taraf lotey aur Sura Baqra shuru kar di. jab eik aadmi ney ye sura padhtey suna to wo jamaat sey peechhey nikal gaya, phir alag namaz padh kar chala gaya. logon ney kaha : aey shakhs ! to munafiq ho gaya hai. us ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main munafiq nahin huwa aur main zarur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jaaunga aur aap ko batlaaunga. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! tehqiq Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) aap key sath namaz padhtey hain, phir hamarey paas aa kar hamari imaamat karatey hain. aur raat aap ney namaz muakhkhar (der) ki to unhoney aap key sath namaz padhi, phir wapis aa kar hamein padhaai aur Sura Baqra shuru kar di. jab mainey ye suna to main (jamaat sey) peechhey nikal gaya aur (alag) namaz padh li. hum oonton par pani dhoney waley log hain. apney haathon sey mehnat kartey hain (itni der tak itni lambi namaz nahin padh saktey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Muaz ! kya to fitne-baaz hai? falan falan sura padha kar."
837,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze khof padhaai. aap ney un logon ko jo aap key peechhey they, do rakaten padhaaein aur jo baad mein aaye unhein bhi do rakaten padhaaein. is tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki chaar rakatein ho gaeen aur un sab ki do do rakaten."
838,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ba-jamaat akeley ki namaz sey sattaais (27) darjey ziyada fazilat rakhti hai."
839,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ba-jamaat akeley ki namaz sey pachchees (25) darjey ziyada fazilat rakhti hai.
840,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ba-jamaat akeley ki namaz sey pachchees (25) darjey ziyada fazilat rakhti hai."
841,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namazi teen aadmi hon to un mein sey eik imaamat karaaey. aur un mein sey imaamat ka ziyada haq daar wo hai jo ziyada qaari ho."
842,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik janib namaz padhi aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) hamarey sath namaz padh rahi thin. aur main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key pehlu mein (daeyn janib) aap key sath namaz padh raha tha.
843,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baain janib khada ho gaya. aap ney mujhey apney baain haath sey pakad kar apni daeyn janib khada kar liya."
844,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik din subah ki namaz padhaai phir farmaya : kya falan shakhs namaz mein hazir hai? logon ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : falan ? logon ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : ye do namazen (Isha aur Fajr) munafiq par intehai bojhal hain. agar wo un ki fazilat jaan lein to zarur hazir hon agar-che ghisat kar aana padey. pehli saf farishton ki saf ki tarah hai. agar tum is ki fazilat jaan lo to tum (is key husool key liye) eik dusrey sey aagey badho. aur aadmi ki namaz eik aur aadmi key sath mil kar akeley ki namaz sey afzal hai. aur do aadmiyon key sath mil kar padhi hui namaz eik aadmi key sath mil kar padhi hui namaz sey afzal hai. aur wo jis qadr ziyada hon utna hi Allah ko ziyada mehbub hai."
845,"Hazrat Utban bin Malik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri qom ki masjid aur merey (ghar key) darmiyan kabhi-kabhi baarishi pani haael rukawat ho jata hai. main chahta hun ke aap merey paas tashrif laaeyn aur merey ghar mein kisi jagah namaz padhein jisey main namaz ki jagah bana lun. aap ney farmaya : hum aisey karengey. jab (agley din) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to puchha : tum kis jagah chahtey ho ke main namaz padhun? mainey ghar key eik koney ki taraf ishara kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye. hamney aap key peechhey saffen baandhin to aap ney hamein do rakatein (nafl) padhaaeen."
846,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz key liye khadey huye to takbire-tahreema kehney sey pehley aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : safen sidhi karo aur aapas mein mil kar khadey ho. main tumhein apney peechhey sey bhi dekhta hun.
847,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (safar mein) they, kisi shakhs ney kaha : agar aap hamein aaram ka moqey ata farmaain (to kya hi achchha ho). aap ney farmaya : mujhey khatra hai ke tum namaz sey soey reh jaaogey. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main tumhara khayal rakhunga. wo let kar so gaey. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni pusht ki tek apni sawari sey laga li. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jaagey to suraj ka kinara tulu ho chuka tha. aap ney farmaya : O' Bilal ! kidhar gaee teri baat? unhoney kaha : aaj jaisi neend to mujhey kabhi nahin aai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney jab chaha tumhari ruhon ko qabz farma liya aur jab chaha wapis kar diya. aey Bilal ! utho logon ko namaz ki ittilaa do. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur Azan kahi phir sab ney wuzu kiya jab ke suraj ooncha aa chuka tha, phir aap uthey aur unhein namaz padhaai."
848,"Ma'daan bin Abu Talha Yaamri sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : mujh sey Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : teri rihaaish-gaah kahan hai? mainey kaha : teiswin key qarib eik basti mein. Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : kisi basti ya sehra mein jo bhi teen aadmi ikhattey rehtey hon aur un mein jamaat qaaim na ki jati ho to yaqin rakho ke un par shetan ghalib aa chuka hai. jamaat qaaim rakho kyonkey bhediya usi bhaid bakri ko khata hai jo rewad sey door rehti hai. Saaib raawi ney kaha ke yahan jamaat sey, namaz ki jamaat murad hai."
849,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! mainey irada kiya ke main endhan (ikhatta kerney) ka hukm dun usey ikhatta kiya jaey, phir hukm dun ke namaz ki Azan kahi jaey, phir eik aadmi ko hukm dun aur wo logon ki imaamat karaaey, phir main un logon ki taraf jaun (jo namaz padhney nahin aaye) aur unkey gharon ko un par jala dun. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar un mein sey koi shakhs jaan ley ke usey charbi wali haddi ya do behtareen khur milengey to wo zarur Isha ki namaz mein hazir hongey."
850,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : jis aadmi ki ye khahish hai ke kal Allah Taala ko (mukammal taur par) Islam ki haalat mein miley to usey paanch namazon ki pabandi us jagah kerni chahiye jahan un ki Azan kahi jaey (yani masjid mein baa-jamaa't). kyonkey Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye hidayat key tareeqey jari farmaaey. tehqiq ye (paanchon) namazeyn (baa-jamaa't masjid mein padhna bhi) hidayat key tariqon mein sey hai. bilashuba main samajhta hun ke ke tum mein sey har eik ney apney ghar mein masjid bana rakhi hai jis mein wo namaz padhta hai. is tarah agar tum gharon mein (farz) namazein padhtey rahey aur masjidon mein jana chhod diya to tum apney Nabi ka (maroof) tariqa chhod bethogey aur agar tum ney Nabi ka tariqa chhod diya to tum gumrah ho jaogey. jo bhi musalman aadmi wuzu karta hai aur achchha wuzu karta hai, phir wo namaz key liye chal kar jata hai to Allah Taala uskey har qadam key iwaz jo wo uthata hai, eik neki likh deta hai ya uski bina par eik darja buland farma deta hai ya uski koi na koi ghalati maaf farma deta hai. mujhey ba-khoobi yad hai ke hum (is wajeh sey) qarib qarib qadam rakha kartey they. aur Allah ki qism ! mujhey achchhi tarah yad hai ke aap key daure-aqdas mein namaz sey koi shakhs peechhey nahin rehta tha magar wo munafiq jis ka nifaq har eik ko malum tha. Allah ki qism ! mainey (us daure-mubarak mein) dekha ke eik aadmi ko do aadmiyon key saharey chala kar masjid mein laya jata tha yahan tak ke usey saf mein khada kar diya jata."
851,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik na-bina aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : mujhey koi haath pakad kar chalaney wala nahin jo mujhey masjid mein namaz key liye laye aur us ney aap sey guzarish ki ke usey ghar mein namaz padhney ki ijazat di jaey. aap ney usey ijazat dey di. jab wo wapis janey key liye muda to aap ney farmaya : tum Azan suntey ho? us ney kaha : ji han, aap ney farmaya : phir (namaz key liye) zarur aao."
852,"Hazrat ibne Ummey Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! tehqiq Madina Munawra mein zahreeley keedey makodey aur darindey bahut hain (lihaza mujhey ghar mein namaz padhney ki ijazat dijiye). aap ney farmaya : kya tum (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ) aur (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح) ki nidaa (awaaz) suntey ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir zarur aao. aur aap ney unhein ghar mein (farz) namaz padhney ki rukhsat (chhoot) nahin di."
853,"Hazrat Urwa sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) apney sathiyon ko jamaat karatey they. eik din namaz ka waqt ho gaya to wo qazaey hajat (peshaab paakhaaney se faraghat) key liye gaey, phir wapis aaye aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs qazaey hajat (peshaab paakhaaney se faraghat) ki zarurat mehsus karey to namaz sey pehley qazaey hajat kar ley."
854,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab raat ka khana ( pak kar) samney aa jaey aur ( udhar ) jamaat khadi ho jaey to pehley khana kha lo."
855,"Hazrat Abu-Mulaih apney walid sey bayan kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hunain mein they ke hum par barish barasney lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan ney aelan kiya ke apney apney khemon mein namaz padh lo."
856,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney wuzu kiya aur achchha wuzu kiya, phir jamaat ki niyat sey masjid ki taraf gaya magar logon ko us haal mein paya ke wo namaz padh chukey hain to Allah Taala uskey liye jamaat mein hazir honey waley jaisa sawab likh deta hai lekin us sey unkey sawab mein kami nahin aati."
857,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna : jis shakhs ney namaz key liye wuzu kiya aur achchha wuzu kiya, phir farz namaz (ki adaaegi key liye masjid) ki taraf chala aur logon key sath ba-jamaat namaz padhi ya (akeley ney) masjid mein padhi Allah Taala uskey liye uskey gunah maaf farma deyga."
858,Hazrat Mihjan (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein they ke namaz ki Azan kahi gaee. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey phir (namaz padh kar) wapis tashrif laye to (dekha ke) Mihjan apni jagah hi mein bethey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhein namaz padhney sey kis chiz ney roka? kya tum musalman aadmi nahin ho? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ! lekin main ghar mein namaz padh aaya hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum masjid mein aao (aur jamaat mil jaey) to logon key sath namaz padho agar-che tum (akeley) namaz padh chukey ho.
859,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aswad Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke mainey Fajr ki namaz Masjide-Khaif mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath padhi. jab aap ney namaz puri farma li to aap ney logon ( namaaziyon ) key aakhir mein do aadmi dekhey jinhoney aap key sath namaz nahin padhi thi. aap ney farmaya : unhein merey paas lao. unhein aap key paas laya gaya to unkey kandhon ka gosht kaanp raha tha. aap ney farmaya : tumhein hamarey sath namaz padhney sey kis chiz ney roka? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum apney gharon mein namaz padh chukey hain. aap ney farmaya : aisa mat karo. jab tum apney gharon mein namaz padh chukey ho, phir tum masjid mein aao aur jamaat pao to unkey sath bhi padh lo. wo (baad wali) tumharey liye nafl ho jaeygi."
860,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney meri raan par haath maartay huye mujh sey farmaya : tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum un logon mein baqi reh jaogey jo namaz ko uskey waqt sey muakhkhar (der) karengey? mainey kaha : aap kya hukm farmatey hain? aap ney farmaya : namaz waqt par padh liya karna phir apna kaam karna phir agar masjid mein tumhari mojudgi key doran mein jamaat shuru ho jaey to padh lena."
861,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key azad karda ghulam Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ko farsh par bethey dekha jab ke log namaz padh rahey they. mainey kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya wajeh hai ke aap namaz nahin padh rahey? unhoney kaha : main namaz padh chuka hun. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna hai : eik namaz din mein do martaba nahin padhi ja sakti.
862,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum namaz key liye aao to dodtey huye na aao balke sukoon aur waqar key sath chaltey huye aao. jo namaz jamaat key sath mil jaey padh lo aur jo reh jaey baad mein puri kar lo.
863,"Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Asr ki namaz padh letey to banu Abdul-Ash'hal key yahaan tashrif ley jatey aur unkey yahan baaten kartey yahan tak ke Maghrib key waqt wapis tashrif latey. Abu-Raafea ney kaha : eik dafa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Maghrib key waqt jaldi aur tezi sey aa rahey they ke hum Baqee sey guzrey to aap ney farmaya : afsos tujh par ! afsos tujh par !. mujhey ye alfaz dil mein bahut takleef deh mehsus huye. main peechhey hat gaya. mainey samjha ke aap mujh sey mukhatib hain. aap ney farmaya : peechhey kyon reh gaey ho? chaltey aao. mainey kaha : mujh sey koi qusur ho gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : kya matlab? mainey kaha : aap ney mujh par izhare-afsos kiya hai. aap ney farmaya : nahin, balke (meri) us baat ka sabab ye hai ke mainey eik aadmi ko falan qabiley ki Zakat leney key liye bheja tha. us ney eik chadar chupa li. ab usey us jaisi aag ki chadar pahnaai gaee hai."
864,Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye riwayat dusri sanad key sath bhi ooper wali riwayat key hum maana manqul hai.
865,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz key liye jaldi aaney waley ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jo eik oont sadqa karta hai. phir jo uskey baad aata hai, wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo gaaey sadqa karta hai. phir uskey baad aaney wala us shakhs ki tarah hai jo eik mendhaa sadqa karta hai. phir jo uskey baad aata hai, wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo murghi sadqa karta hai. phir jo uskey baad aata hai, wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo andaa sadqa karta hai."
866,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to us (baa-jamaa't) farz key ilawa koi aur namaz nahin.
867,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to farz namaz key ilawa koi namaz nahin."
868,Hazrat ibne Baheena (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke subah ki namaz ki iqaamat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko namaz padhtey dekha jab ke muazzan iqaamat keh raha tha. aap ney farmaya : to subah ki namaz chaar rakat padheyga?
869,Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz padha rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya. us ney do rakatein padhein phir namaz mein shamil huwa. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to aap ney farmaya : Oo falan ! teri kon si namaz moatabar hai? wo jo tu ney hamarey sath padhi ya wo jo tu ney akeley padhi?
870,Hazrat Anas Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey ghar tashrif laye. main aur hamarey eik yatim ney aap key peechhey khadey ho kar namaz padhi aur (humari walida) Hazrat Ummey Sulem (Raziallahu anha) ney hamarey peechhey namaz padhi.
871,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu Anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik bahut khoobsurat aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey namaz padha karti thi. kuchh  (nek) log qasdan pehli saf mein khadey hotey they taake wo nazar na aaye. aur kuchh (munafiq qisam key) log jaan-boojh kar peechhey rehtey they yahan tak ke aakhiri saf mein khadey hotey (taake usey dekhen). phir jab rukoo kartey to baghal key nichey sey usey dekhtey they. Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (ولقد علمنا المستقدمین منکم ولقد علمنا المستاخرین),''hum khub jantey hain tum mein sey aagey rehney walon ko aur khub jantey hain peechhey rehney walon ko."
872,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo (eik dafa) masjid mein dakhil huye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rukoo ki haalat mein they, chunanche unhoney saf sey peechhey hi rukoo kar liya (aur rukoo hi ki haalat mein chal kar saf mein pahunchey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (namaz key baad farmaya : Allah Taala tumhari (neki ki) hirs mein izafa farmaai lekin dobara aisey na karna."
873,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik din namaz padhaai. Salam pher kar mudey to farmaya : aey falan ! to apni namaz achchhi tarah nahin padhta. kya namazi khud ghor nahin karta ke wo kaisey namaz padh raha hai? mein tumhein peechhey bhi aisey dekhta hun jaisey main aagey dekhta hun.
874,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar sey pehley do rakat aur baad mein do rakat padhtey they. aur Maghrib key baad ghar mein do rakat aur Isha key baad do rakat padhtey they. aur Jumey key baad namaz nahin padhtey they yahan tak ke ghar ja kar do rakat padhtey.
875,"Hazrat Aasim bin Zamra ney kaha ke hamney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki nafl namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : tum mein sey kon uski taqat rakhta hai? hamney kaha : agar hum karney ki taqat nahin rakhtey to kam se kam sun to lein. aap ney farmaya : jab suraj us (mashriq ki) taraf itna ooncha hota jitna ke wo us (maghrib ki) taraf mein Asr key waqt hota hai to aap do rakatein padhtey aur jab suraj us (mashriq ki) taraf itna hota jitna wo us (Maghrib ki) taraf Zohar key waqt hota hai to chaar rakat padhtey aur Zohar sey pehley chaar rakat aur baad mein do rakat padhtey aur Asr sey pehley is tarah chaar rakat padhtey ke har do rakat key baad (tashahud mein) muqarrab farishton, anbiya aur un ki perwi karney waley mominon aur musalmanon par salam padhtey."
876,"Aasim bin Zamra sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib sey din mein farz namaz sey qabl Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey kon uski taqat rakhta hai? phir hamein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do rakat padhtey they jab suraj kuchh ooncha aa jata tha. aur nisfunnahaar (wo waqt jabki suraj bilkul oopar aa jaata) sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey salam aakhir mein phertey (do rakat key baad salam na phertey)."
